The paper focuses on image deblurring, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). Additionally, the paper proposes a novel model that incorporates semantic information, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of GANs for image deblurring also falls under multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper mentions image captioning, which is a task in natural language processing (cs.CL).
